{
  "video_id": "lPtPG2lAmm4",
  "title": "How diversity makes teams more innovative | Roc√≠o Lorenzo",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13640.0,
      "end_time": 14896.0,
      "text": "Fifteen years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14920.0,
      "end_time": 19759.0,
      "text": "I thought that the diversity stuff was not something I had to worry about."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20480.0,
      "end_time": 23720.0,
      "text": "It was something an older generation had to fight for."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24960.0,
      "end_time": 28656.0,
      "text": "In my university, we were 50-50, male-female,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28680.0,
      "end_time": 31456.0,
      "text": "and we women often had better grades."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31480.0,
      "end_time": 34856.0,
      "text": "So while not everything was perfect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34880.0,
      "end_time": 36896.0,
      "text": "diversity and leadership decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36920.0,
      "end_time": 41000.0,
      "text": "was something that would happen naturally over time, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42640.0,
      "end_time": 44400.0,
      "text": "Well, not quite."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45160.0,
      "end_time": 48560.0,
      "text": "While moving up the ladder working as a management consultant"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48800.0,
      "end_time": 50135.0,
      "text": "across Europe and the US,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50160.0,
      "end_time": 54736.0,
      "text": "I started to realize how often I was the only woman in the room"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54760.0,
      "end_time": 58280.0,
      "text": "and how homogenous leadership still is."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59520.0,
      "end_time": 61336.0,
      "text": "Many leaders I met"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61360.0,
      "end_time": 66176.0,
      "text": "saw diversity as something to comply with out of political correctness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66200.0,
      "end_time": 68840.0,
      "text": "or, best case, the right thing to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69680.0,
      "end_time": 71680.0,
      "text": "but not as a business priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 72320.0,
      "end_time": 74655.0,
      "text": "They just did not have a reason to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74680.0,
      "end_time": 79656.0,
      "text": "that diversity would help them achieve their most immediate, pressing goals:"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79680.0,
      "end_time": 82736.0,
      "text": "hitting the numbers, delivering the new product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82760.0,
      "end_time": 85400.0,
      "text": "the real goals they are measured by."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86440.0,
      "end_time": 89856.0,
      "text": "My personal experience working with diverse teams"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 89880.0,
      "end_time": 93976.0,
      "text": "had been that while they require a little bit more effort at the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94000.0,
      "end_time": 97200.0,
      "text": "they did bring fresher, more creative ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97880.0,
      "end_time": 100150.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100400.0,
      "end_time": 103856.0,
      "text": "Are diverse organizations really more innovative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 103880.0,
      "end_time": 107720.0,
      "text": "and can diversity be more than something to comply with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108320.0,
      "end_time": 110679.0,
      "text": "Can it be a real competitive advantage?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112360.0,
      "end_time": 116640.0,
      "text": "So to find out, we set up a study with the Technical University of Munich."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 117400.0,
      "end_time": 122576.0,
      "text": "We surveyed 171 companies in Germany, Austria and Switzerland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 122600.0,
      "end_time": 125536.0,
      "text": "and as we speak, we&#39;re expanding the study"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125560.0,
      "end_time": 128376.0,
      "text": "to 1,600 companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 128400.0,
      "end_time": 130880.0,
      "text": "in five additional countries around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131760.0,
      "end_time": 134655.0,
      "text": "We asked those companies basically two things:"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 134680.0,
      "end_time": 137720.0,
      "text": "how innovative they are and how diverse they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 138840.0,
      "end_time": 140336.0,
      "text": "To measure the first one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 140360.0,
      "end_time": 143800.0,
      "text": "we asked them about innovation revenue."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 144000.0,
      "end_time": 146656.0,
      "text": "Innovation revenue is the share of revenues they&#39;ve made"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 146680.0,
      "end_time": 149696.0,
      "text": "from new products and services in the last three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149720.0,
      "end_time": 152976.0,
      "text": "meaning we did not ask them how many creative ideas they have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 153000.0,
      "end_time": 156816.0,
      "text": "but rather if these ideas translate into products and services"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156840.0,
      "end_time": 160240.0,
      "text": "that really make the company more successful today and tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 161760.0,
      "end_time": 166296.0,
      "text": "To measure diversity, we looked at six different factors:"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 166320.0,
      "end_time": 169880.0,
      "text": "country of origin, age and gender, amongst others."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 171320.0,
      "end_time": 174256.0,
      "text": "While preparing to go in the field with those questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 174280.0,
      "end_time": 176536.0,
      "text": "I sat down with my team"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 176560.0,
      "end_time": 179840.0,
      "text": "and we discussed what we would expect as a result."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 181640.0,
      "end_time": 183760.0,
      "text": "To put it mildly, we were not optimistic."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 185000.0,
      "end_time": 188536.0,
      "text": "The most skeptical person on the team thought, or saw a real possibility,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 188560.0,
      "end_time": 190960.0,
      "text": "that we would find nothing at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 192360.0,
      "end_time": 194656.0,
      "text": "Most of the team was rather on the cautious side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 194680.0,
      "end_time": 198576.0,
      "text": "so we landed all together at \"only if,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 198600.0,
      "end_time": 200696.0,
      "text": "meaning that we might find some kind of link"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 200720.0,
      "end_time": 203256.0,
      "text": "between innovation and diversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 203280.0,
      "end_time": 204936.0,
      "text": "but not across the board --"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 204960.0,
      "end_time": 207856.0,
      "text": "rather only if certain criteria are met,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 207880.0,
      "end_time": 211936.0,
      "text": "for example leadership style, very open leadership style"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 211960.0,
      "end_time": 216120.0,
      "text": "that allowed people to speak up freely and safely and contribute."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 218240.0,
      "end_time": 220280.0,
      "text": "A couple of months later, the data came in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 221520.0,
      "end_time": 225840.0,
      "text": "and the results convinced the most skeptical amongst us."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 226560.0,
      "end_time": 228416.0,
      "text": "The answer was a clear yes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 228440.0,
      "end_time": 230200.0,
      "text": "no ifs, no buts."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 230840.0,
      "end_time": 232976.0,
      "text": "The data in our sample showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 233000.0,
      "end_time": 237480.0,
      "text": "that more diverse companies are simply more innovative, period."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 239120.0,
      "end_time": 244136.0,
      "text": "Now, a fair question to ask is the chicken or the egg question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 244160.0,
      "end_time": 247576.0,
      "text": "meaning, are companies really more innovative"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 247600.0,
      "end_time": 250256.0,
      "text": "because they have a more diverse leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 250280.0,
      "end_time": 251536.0,
      "text": "or the other way around?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 251560.0,
      "end_time": 252760.0,
      "text": "Which way is it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 253280.0,
      "end_time": 257400.0,
      "text": "Now, we do not know how much is correlation versus causation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 257880.0,
      "end_time": 260856.0,
      "text": "but what we do know is that clearly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 260880.0,
      "end_time": 264560.0,
      "text": "in our sample, companies that are more diverse"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 264800.0,
      "end_time": 265575.0,
      "text": "are more innovative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 265600.0,
      "end_time": 267896.0,
      "text": "and that companies that are more innovative"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 267920.0,
      "end_time": 269760.0,
      "text": "have more diverse leadership, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 270279.0,
      "end_time": 273160.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s fair to assume that it works both ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 273400.0,
      "end_time": 276920.0,
      "text": "diversity driving innovation and innovation driving diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 279360.0,
      "end_time": 282136.0,
      "text": "Now, once we published the results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 282160.0,
      "end_time": 286736.0,
      "text": "we were surprised about the reactions in the media."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 286760.0,
      "end_time": 289656.0,
      "text": "We got quite some attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 289680.0,
      "end_time": 292176.0,
      "text": "And it went from quite factual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 292200.0,
      "end_time": 296456.0,
      "text": "like \"Higher Female Share Boosts Innovation\""
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 296480.0,
      "end_time": 299976.0,
      "text": "to a little bit more sensationalist."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 300000.0,
      "end_time": 301936.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 301960.0,
      "end_time": 303176.0,
      "text": "As you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303200.0,
      "end_time": 306296.0,
      "text": "\"Stay-at-home Women Cost Trillions,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 306320.0,
      "end_time": 308256.0,
      "text": "and, my personal favorite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 308280.0,
      "end_time": 310655.0,
      "text": "\"Housewives Kill Innovation.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 310680.0,
      "end_time": 313696.0,
      "text": "Well, there&#39;s no such thing as bad publicity, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 313720.0,
      "end_time": 316560.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 316800.0,
      "end_time": 318560.0,
      "text": "On the back of that coverage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 318800.0,
      "end_time": 321536.0,
      "text": "we started to get calls from senior executives"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 321560.0,
      "end_time": 323256.0,
      "text": "wanting to understand more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 323280.0,
      "end_time": 326840.0,
      "text": "especially -- surprise, surprise -- about gender diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 327680.0,
      "end_time": 331776.0,
      "text": "I tend to open up those discussions by asking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 331800.0,
      "end_time": 335936.0,
      "text": "\"Well, what do you think of the situation in your organization today?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 335960.0,
      "end_time": 338520.0,
      "text": "And a frequent reaction to that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 339480.0,
      "end_time": 342520.0,
      "text": "\"Well, we&#39;re not yet there, but we&#39;re not that bad.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 343240.0,
      "end_time": 345416.0,
      "text": "One executive told me, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 345440.0,
      "end_time": 346976.0,
      "text": "\"Oh, we&#39;re not that bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 347000.0,
      "end_time": 349736.0,
      "text": "We have one member in our board who is a woman.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 349760.0,
      "end_time": 351960.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 351120.0,
      "end_time": 352336.0,
      "text": "And you laugh --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 352360.0,
      "end_time": 355320.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 358760.0,
      "end_time": 362135.0,
      "text": "Now, you laugh, but he had a point in being proud about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 362160.0,
      "end_time": 363496.0,
      "text": "because in Germany,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 363520.0,
      "end_time": 366496.0,
      "text": "if you have a company"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 366520.0,
      "end_time": 369960.0,
      "text": "and it has one member on the board who is a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 369120.0,
      "end_time": 371536.0,
      "text": "you are part of a select group of 30"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 371560.0,
      "end_time": 375216.0,
      "text": "out of the 100 largest publicly listed companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 375240.0,
      "end_time": 380456.0,
      "text": "The other 70 companies have an all-male board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 380480.0,
      "end_time": 384296.0,
      "text": "and not even one of these hundred largest publicly listed companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 384320.0,
      "end_time": 388000.0,
      "text": "have, as of today, a female CEO."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 389800.0,
      "end_time": 391320.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the critically important insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392240.0,
      "end_time": 396216.0,
      "text": "Those few female board members alone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 396240.0,
      "end_time": 398136.0,
      "text": "they won&#39;t make a difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398160.0,
      "end_time": 402280.0,
      "text": "Our data shows that for gender diversity to have an impact on innovation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 403200.0,
      "end_time": 406920.0,
      "text": "you need to have more than 20 percent women in leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 407480.0,
      "end_time": 409800.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look at the numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 410600.0,
      "end_time": 414296.0,
      "text": "As you can see, we divided the sample into three groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 414320.0,
      "end_time": 417216.0,
      "text": "and the results are quite dramatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 417240.0,
      "end_time": 421936.0,
      "text": "Only in the group where you have more than 20 percent women in leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 421960.0,
      "end_time": 425840.0,
      "text": "only then you see a clear jump in innovation revenue"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 426840.0,
      "end_time": 428816.0,
      "text": "to above-average levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 428840.0,
      "end_time": 433496.0,
      "text": "So experience and data shows that you do need critical mass"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 433520.0,
      "end_time": 435150.0,
      "text": "to move the needle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 435400.0,
      "end_time": 438376.0,
      "text": "and companies like Alibaba, JP Morgan or Apple"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 438400.0,
      "end_time": 441760.0,
      "text": "have as of today already achieved that threshold."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 444480.0,
      "end_time": 446880.0,
      "text": "Another reaction I got quite a lot was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 448520.0,
      "end_time": 451400.0,
      "text": "\"Well, it will get solved over time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 452200.0,
      "end_time": 455455.0,
      "text": "And I have all the sympathy in the world for that point of view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 455480.0,
      "end_time": 457400.0,
      "text": "because I used to think like that, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 458600.0,
      "end_time": 461896.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s have a look here again and look at the numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 461920.0,
      "end_time": 464560.0,
      "text": "taking Germany as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 464800.0,
      "end_time": 466296.0,
      "text": "Let me first give you the good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 466320.0,
      "end_time": 469135.0,
      "text": "So the share of women who are college graduates"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 469160.0,
      "end_time": 472576.0,
      "text": "and have at least 10 years of professional experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 472600.0,
      "end_time": 475896.0,
      "text": "has grown nicely over the last 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 475920.0,
      "end_time": 479696.0,
      "text": "which means the pool in which to fish for female leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 479720.0,
      "end_time": 481856.0,
      "text": "has increased over time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 481880.0,
      "end_time": 483576.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s great."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 483600.0,
      "end_time": 485440.0,
      "text": "Now, according to my old theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 486880.0,
      "end_time": 488456.0,
      "text": "the share of women in leadership"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 488480.0,
      "end_time": 490800.0,
      "text": "would have grown more or less in parallel, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 491840.0,
      "end_time": 494719.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s have a look at what happened in reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 495480.0,
      "end_time": 497400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not even close,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 499360.0,
      "end_time": 502576.0,
      "text": "which means I was so wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 502600.0,
      "end_time": 505376.0,
      "text": "and which means that my generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 505400.0,
      "end_time": 506599.0,
      "text": "your generation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 507680.0,
      "end_time": 511200.0,
      "text": "the best-educated female generation in history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 512520.0,
      "end_time": 513936.0,
      "text": "we have just not made it."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 513960.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518456.00000000006,
      "text": "We have failed to achieve leadership in significant numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 518480.0,
      "end_time": 521400.0,
      "text": "Education just did not translate into leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 522720.0,
      "end_time": 525816.0,
      "text": "Now, that was a painful realization for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 525840.0,
      "end_time": 527976.0,
      "text": "and made me realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 528000.0,
      "end_time": 530296.0,
      "text": "if we want to change this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 530320.0,
      "end_time": 532679.0,
      "text": "we need to engage, and we need to do better."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 534200.0,
      "end_time": 536560.0,
      "text": "Now, what to do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 537320.0,
      "end_time": 540856.0,
      "text": "Achieving more than 20 percent women in leadership"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 540880.0,
      "end_time": 543256.0,
      "text": "seems like a daunting task to many,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 543280.0,
      "end_time": 545760.0,
      "text": "understandably, given the track record."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 547800.0,
      "end_time": 548296.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s doable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 548320.0,
      "end_time": 551576.0,
      "text": "and there are many companies today that are making progress there"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 551600.0,
      "end_time": 553216.0,
      "text": "and doing it successfully."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 553240.0,
      "end_time": 556696.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take SAP, the software company, as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 556720.0,
      "end_time": 561376.0,
      "text": "They had, in 2011, 19 percent women in leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 561400.0,
      "end_time": 563256.0,
      "text": "yet they decided to do better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 563280.0,
      "end_time": 566456.0,
      "text": "and they did what you do in any other area of business"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 566480.0,
      "end_time": 568160.0,
      "text": "where you want to improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 568400.0,
      "end_time": 570520.0,
      "text": "They set themselves a measurable target."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 571440.0,
      "end_time": 576336.0,
      "text": "So they set themselves a target of 25 percent for 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 576360.0,
      "end_time": 577960.0,
      "text": "which they have just achieved."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 579120.0,
      "end_time": 582536.0,
      "text": "The goals made them think more creatively about developing leaders"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 582560.0,
      "end_time": 585160.0,
      "text": "and tapping new recruiting pools."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 585400.0,
      "end_time": 589400.0,
      "text": "They now even set a target of 30 percent women in leadership for 2022."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 590480.0,
      "end_time": 592936.0,
      "text": "So experience shows it&#39;s doable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 592960.0,
      "end_time": 594936.0,
      "text": "and at the end of the day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 594960.0,
      "end_time": 599960.0,
      "text": "it all boils down to two decisions that are taken every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 599120.0,
      "end_time": 601880.0,
      "text": "in every organization by many of us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 603640.0,
      "end_time": 607400.0,
      "text": "who to hire and who to develop and promote."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 608000.0,
      "end_time": 610576.0,
      "text": "Now, nothing against women&#39;s programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 610600.0,
      "end_time": 612936.0,
      "text": "networks, mentoring, trainings."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 612960.0,
      "end_time": 614160.0,
      "text": "All is good."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 615320.0,
      "end_time": 617256.0,
      "text": "But it is these two decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 617280.0,
      "end_time": 621295.0,
      "text": "that at the end of the day send the most powerful change signal"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 621320.0,
      "end_time": 622840.0,
      "text": "in any organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 625400.0,
      "end_time": 628960.0,
      "text": "Now, I never set out to be a diversity advocate."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 628120.0,
      "end_time": 629840.0,
      "text": "I am a business advisor."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 630720.0,
      "end_time": 635696.0,
      "text": "But now my goal is to change the face of leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 635720.0,
      "end_time": 637160.0,
      "text": "to make it more diverse --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 638800.0,
      "end_time": 640576.0,
      "text": "and not so that leaders can check a box"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 640600.0,
      "end_time": 643576.0,
      "text": "and feel like they have complied with something"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 643600.0,
      "end_time": 646136.0,
      "text": "or they have been politically correct."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 646160.0,
      "end_time": 647856.0,
      "text": "But because they understand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 647880.0,
      "end_time": 651376.0,
      "text": "they understand that diversity is making their organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 651400.0,
      "end_time": 652800.0,
      "text": "more innovative, better."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 653680.0,
      "end_time": 657536.0,
      "text": "And by embracing diversity, by embracing diverse talent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 657560.0,
      "end_time": 659880.0,
      "text": "we are providing true opportunity for everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 660520.0,
      "end_time": 662175.0,
      "text": "Thank you. Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 662200.0,
      "end_time": 664840.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}